[contrast theme description]: Koresha itandukaniro rinini cyane ryamabara kugirango wongere itandukaniro ryamasomo kandi byoroshye gusoma. Insanganyamatsiko ihabanye cyane ikoresha palette ntoya yamabara atandukanye (nkubururu bwijimye) yorohereza interineti kubona, mugihe ukomeje kwemeza ko ushobora kwishimira igishushanyo cyiza cyamasomo ya Easygenerator
[readable font description]: Hitamo "Gusoma Imyandikire" kugirango ukoreshe shingiro, yoroshye kandi idashushanyijeho imyandikire ya Arial kumasomo. Arial nta mitako yinyongera cyangwa itera imbere bigatuma iba imwe muburyo bworoshye kandi bworoshye gusoma imyandikire
[font size adjustment description]: "Imihindukire y'ubunini bwinyandiko"igushoboza kongera cyangwa kugabanya ingano yinyandiko utarinze kwiyegereza ibindi byose kurupapuro. Ushobora guhinduranya byoroshye hagati ya nshingirwaho, bini, bini cyane, nubunini cyane bwimyandikire y'ibirimo ukanda kuri buto (+) na (-)
[dyslexia font description]: Koresha imyandikire yabugenewe "Dyslexia" kugirango wongere inyuguti igaragara. Iyi myandikire yorohereza gutandukanya imiterere yinyuguti ninyuguti zitandukanye kandi itanga uburambe bwo gusoma
[seizure safe description]: Emeza uburyo bwa "Rinda guta ubwenjye" kugirango ugabanye animasiyo namabara amurika cyane mu mashusho na videwo.
